product_description: Looking for a snack that is an excellent source of protein, high fiber, and keto friendly? Introducing KIND Protein MAX Crispy Chocolate Peanut Butter Snack Bars. Protein Max bars are individually wrapped, gluten free, and contain 20g of protein, 0g added sugar*, and 1g of total sugar. These ready to eat high protein snacks are not just about hitting your protein goals; they're a delicious celebration of real ingredients, like our number one ingredient, nutrient-dense peanuts. Kickstart your busy mornings with the balanced nutrition and convenience of KIND Protein MAX bars! Your perfect on-the-go protein bar snack that is high in fiber and deliciously satisfying. From conquering hiking trails to refueling post-workout, skip the trail mix and opt for KIND’s 250 calorie KIND Protein Max snack bars to jump start your adventure-filled day. Embrace the delectable taste of chocolate combined with heart healthy peanuts in KIND Protein MAX keto friendly protein bar. Join us in creating a kinder AND healthier world—one act, one snack at a time. Healthy snacks are smarter snacks. Snack KIND! (Not a Low Calorie Food.
